ComicInfo.Series: Bettie Page and the Alien Agenda
ComicInfo.Summary: Bettie and her team are getting closer to the final location of the alien weapon stockpile as they slash their way through the jungles of Mexico. But questions start to arise as to what they might really be searching for. Are aliens really hiding weapons? Could it be something much worse? It's time to confront the beauty, and the terror, in the land of the Ancient Aztecs. Let's see if our team is prepared...and what Young-ja brought to eat this time!
